And one for configuration in hive-default.xml for setting up default job tracker:

&#060;property&#062;
    &#060;name&#062;mapred.jpd.tracker&#060;/name&#062;
    &#060;value&#062;localhost:9001&#060;/value&#062;
&#060;/property&#062;

Put following lines into hive-default.xml:

&#060;property&#062;
    &#060;name&#062;hive.aux.jars.path&#060;/name&#062;
    &#060;value&#062;file:///opt/hive/lib/hive-contrib-0.7.1.jar&#060;/value&#062;
&#060;/property&#062;

so that I can get rid of running &quot;add jar ...&quot; every time.

Every time I have to run this under Hive:

